notes: Cartoon about the high cost of living in Africa, with an stereotyped missionary and African.

116.title: "High Death!" 5 p. in He-Man, no. 2
116.author: [No author]
notes: Summary: A circus aerialist is on a high bridge planning a suicide jump, and a policeman climbs up to talk her down. "You're young! You're pretty! You've got everything to live for!" Then another aerialist comes along and tries to kill them both.

118.title: "A High Draft Choice"
118.author: Millar-Hinds.
notes: Summary: The Smashers' general manager looks like an idiot after his car is stolen by a new player with a criminal record from college.
